  <description>
    <p>
      Krokiet is a multi functional that findsduplicates, empty folders, similar images, broken files etc.
      - duplicates
      - empty folders
      - similar images
      - broken files
      - temporary files
      - empty files
      - big files
      - invalid symlinks
      - similar music files
      - similar videos
      - videos that could be cropped/optimized
      - exif tags in files
    </p>
